Change a configuration property on this object to the value specified.
Change a configuration property on this object to the value specified and return the previous value that the configuration property was set to (or null if it was not previously set). If newVal is null, set the property to its default value;
If the property cannot be changed, throw a {@link ReconfigurationException}.

     {@inheritDoc}

This method makes the change to this objects {@link Configuration}
and calls reconfigurePropertyImpl to update internal data structures.
This method cannot be overridden, subclasses should instead override
reconfigureProperty.

